      <title>土耳其不顾抗议通过新法，扑杀流浪狗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/turkey-passes-new-law-to-curb-street-dogs-despite-mass-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其通过了一项有争议的法案，为扑杀数百万只流浪狗铺平了道路，引发了伊斯坦布尔和安卡拉等以流浪狗众多而闻名的地区的抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/turkey-passes-new-law-to-curb-street-dogs-despite-mass-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
