    <item>
      <title>韩国在美贸易协定中发挥主导作用或有助于限制芯片争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/south-korea-taps-us-trade-deal-to-prevent-chip-spats-with-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国将在美国主导的亚洲贸易协定中发挥引领作用，通过合作网络确保全球供应链的安全，这一作用也可能有助于限制与日本发生贸易争端的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/south-korea-taps-us-trade-deal-to-prevent-chip-spats-with-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
